TopicTitle: FPS Very low when running KSP with mods

Articles.Content:
My FPS drops from around 100FPS to about 24FPS when I load it up with mods. I got a GSync Monitor and im running KSP in 64Bit Mode

 

Specs of my PC:
 

Spoiler

 

I7 4790K

GTX980

Samsung 250Gb SSD

WD 2TB Black HDD

MSI Gaming 7

H100i GTX

HyperX Fury 16Gb
